UMNTWANA uNhlanganiso Zulu, oyizinyane leSilo, ukhuthaza amadoda ukuthi abaphe abantu besifazane imali ngemva kwenkonzo yasekamelweni. UMntwana uNhlanganiso uthi kuyichilo ukuthi kunamadoda aba madolonzima uma kukhulunywa ngokupha abantu besifazane imali. Ubekhuluma lapho obekubuthene khona amadoda kwa-AA, ehholo eMlaza eningizimu yeTheku.  “Madoda kumele nazi ukuthi abantu besifazane bayaphiwa imali futhi benjalo nje bayayithanda. Musani ukuncishana nemali kubantu besifazane. Anazi yini ukuthi abantu besifazane bayathanda ukudla imali yamadoda abo? UMntwana uthe akafuni nokuyizwa eyamadoda agcina ngokuthi ‘ngiyabonga’ nje kuphela kumuntu wesifazane ngemuva kwenkonzo yasekamelweni. “Amanye amadoda acabanga ukuthi afanelwe ukuthola ucansi kanti akunjalo. Uma uyindoda uluthola ucansi ubojabula ungangcini ngakho ebese uyabonga kuloyo phela okusizile wakupha lona,’’ usho kanjena. Eqhuba uthe akafuni nokuyizwa indaba yamadoda azishaya isifuba ngokuthi yiwona aphiwa imali ngabantu besifazane. Uthe kuyichilo nje! “Indoda yiyona epha umuntu wesifazane imali hhayi ukuthi indoda iphiwe ngowesifazane. Njengoba wena ndoda uphiwa ngumuntu wesifazane imali uyazi yini ukuthi naye ukupha imali ayithathe kwenye indoda?” Uphethe ngokunxusa amadoda ukuba azazi futhi azihloniphe ukuze aphile impilo engcono. Uwakhuthaze ngokuthi azijwayeze ukuhambela odokotela ahlolele izifo ezahlukene. Kulo mbuthano kudingidwe nezinye izihloko okubalwa kuzo izingqinamba ezibhekena namadoda kulesi sikhathi okubalwa ukungabi khona kwamathuba omsebenzi, nodlame olubhekiswe kwabesifazane.